<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="gsz0760b07shiYiFu"><lb
n="0760b07" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0760b07"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042410">京兆慈恩寺</placeName><persName key="A008784">義福</persName>傳（<persName key="A003666">行思</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0760b08"/><persName key="A008784">釋義福</persName>，姓姜氏，<placeName key="PL000000004308">潞州銅鞮</placeName>人也。幼慕空門，<lb
ed="T" n="0760b09"/>黍累世務，初止<placeName key="PL000000042560">藍田化感寺</placeName>，處方丈之室<lb
ed="T" n="0760b10"/>凡二十餘年，未甞出房宇之外。後隷<placeName key="PL000000042410">京師慈<lb
ed="T" n="0760b11"/>恩寺</placeName>，道望高峙，傾動物心。<date from-iso="0723-02-14" key="j19851741985528" to-iso="0724-02-03">開元十一年</date>，從<ref type="person" target="#A000291">駕</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0760b12"/>往<placeName key="PL000000023581">東都</placeName>，經<placeName key="PL000000005199">蒲</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000025169"><anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz4"/>虢<anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz4"/></placeName>二州，刺史及官吏士女皆<lb
ed="T" n="0760b13"/>齎旛花迎<ref type="person" target="#A008784">之</ref>，所在途路充塞，拜<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz5"/>紛紛，瞻<lb
ed="T" n="0760b14"/>望無厭。以<date from-iso="0732-02-05" key="j19884521988806" to-iso="0733-01-24">二十年</date>卒，有制諡號曰<persName key="A008784">大智禪<lb
ed="T" n="0760b15"/>師</persName>，葬<anchor xml:id="beg0760002"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0760002"/><placeName key="PL000000023845">伊闕</placeName>之北。送葬者數萬人。中書侍<lb
ed="T" n="0760b16"/>郎<persName key="A010205">嚴<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz6"/>挺<anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz6"/>之</persName>躬行喪服，若弟子焉，又撰碑文。<lb
ed="T" n="0760b17"/><persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>禪門之傑，雖有禪行，得帝王重之無<lb
ed="T" n="0760b18"/>以加者，而未甞聚徒開法也。洎乎<persName key="A009319">普寂</persName>始<lb
ed="T" n="0760b19"/>於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189 #PL000000023581">都城</ref>傳教二十餘載，人皆仰<ref type="person" target="#A008784">之</ref>。初<persName key="A008784">福</persName>往<lb
ed="T" n="0760b20"/><placeName key="PL000000023581">東洛</placeName>，召其徒戒其終期，兵部侍郎<persName key="A010207">張均</persName>、太<lb
ed="T" n="0760b21"/>尉<persName key="A010069">房琯</persName>、禮部侍郎<persName key="A010209">韋陟</persName>常所信重，是日皆預<lb
ed="T" n="0760b22"/>造焉。<persName key="A008784">福</persName>乃升堂，為門人演說，且曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A008784">吾</ref>沒日<lb
ed="T" n="0760b23"/>昃，當為此決別耳。」久之，<persName key="A010207">張</persName>謂<persName key="A010069">房</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010207">某</ref>夙歲<lb
ed="T" n="0760b24"/>餌金丹，未甞臨喪。」言訖，<persName key="A010207">張</persName>遂潛去。<persName key="A008784">福</persName>忽謂<lb
ed="T" n="0760b25"/><persName key="A010069">房</persName>曰：「與<ref type="person" target="#A010207">張公</ref>遊有年矣。<ref type="person" target="#A010207">張公</ref>將有非常之<lb
ed="T" n="0760b26"/>咎，名節皆虧。向來若終此法會，足以免禍。<lb
ed="T" n="0760b27"/>惜哉！」乃提<persName key="A010069">房</persName>手曰：「必為中興名臣，其勉之！」<lb
ed="T" n="0760b28"/>言訖而終。後<persName key="A010207">張均</persName>陷<ref type="person" target="#A008454">賊</ref>庭也，受其偽官，而<lb
ed="T" n="0760b29"/><persName key="A010069">房</persName>翼戴<ref type="person" target="#A000291 #A004378">兩朝</ref>，畢立大節，皆終<persName key="A008784">福</persName>之言矣。又<pb ed="T" n="0760c" xml:id="T50.2061.0760c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0760c01"/><persName key="A003666">釋行思</persName>，姓劉氏，<placeName key="PL000000019384">廬陵</placeName>人也。濡潤厥躬，貞諒<lb
ed="T" n="0760c02"/>其性。出塵之後，納戒已還，破觚求圓，斵雕<lb
ed="T" n="0760c03"/>為朴，厥志天然也。往<placeName key="PL000000030617">韶陽</placeName>見<persName key="A001719">大鑒禪師</persName>，一<lb
ed="T" n="0760c04"/>言蔽斷，猶擊蒙焉。既了本心，地祇迭告還，<lb
ed="T" n="0760c05"/>復<placeName key="PL000000019383">吉州</placeName>闡化，四方禪客繁擁其堂。<date key="j19917121991712" when-iso="0741-01-08">開元二<lb
ed="T" n="0760c06"/>十八年十二月十三日</date>入滅于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000019384">本生地</ref>，勅諡<lb
ed="T" n="0760c07"/>大師，號曰<persName key="A003666">洪濟</persName>，塔曰歸真。其塔<date from-iso="0841" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="0846">會昌中</date>例<lb
ed="T" n="0760c08"/>從堙毀，後法嗣者重崇樹之。</p>
